University of Ilorin, UNILORIN business school professional postgraduate programmes admission form for the 2018/2019 academic session is now on sale. The management of the Ilorin Business School (IBS), University of Ilorin (UNILORIN) invite applications from suitably qualified candidates for admission into their various Professional Postgraduate programmes for the 2018/2019 academic session. The post UNILORIN Business School Postgraduate Form for 2019/2020 Session appeared first on Nigerian Scholars. Source: Nigerian Scholars